<br>
Freeport can be a confusing zone, when you arrive from the docks, make sure you head to East Freeport before heading out of the town. This will take you to the Commonlands instead of the desert.  <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=381929"> Naladini </a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
