<br>
For me, my journey was to Erudin, starting from Freeport, and happened before that neat thing of items returning with you to your bind point. Was always a thing for me to have all my spells for my level, and rather than bind along the way (I was level 12), I wanted to be able to gate back quickly to familiar hunting grounds.<br>
<br>
My trek took me through Rivervale and the Beholder's Maze. I had been advised that High Pass was definately less than safe, though in retrospect, it was probably safer than risking the Maze. I remember many a time watching invis blink on me with monsters about, and having to duck behind a rock, hoping they didn't see me while I recast it. <br>
<br>
West Karana, I always followed the path. There's not too much danger there if you stay invis, and avoid the bandit patrol on the path. My philosophy was simple. If it's not a tree, avoid it, and even then, be wary of the trees. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  West Karana is sparsly populated enough to be able to see only random creatures and no camps along the path. Just keep going west (Sense heading is a boon).<br>
<br>
Kithicor, however, always had me on edge. During nighttime, that misty fog hides much, and undead see all (to me they did). And, at level 12, with these creatures easily more than double my level, I'd be smoked human steaks before I knew what hit me. Speaking of that, too, never sit and wait for daylight to come inside Kithicor. Any roamers nearby Rivervale (for example) might have this nasty tendancy to Harmtouch you (opposite of a paladin's Lay on Hands heal). Let me tell you, at low levels, a 500 pt harmtouch is easily more than a match for a fledgling mage.<br>
<br>
I miss the days of being so in awe at the world. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://&quot;http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886&quot;"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.ninjacorp.com/Rhasin_sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#333333>- </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower>The Magician's Tower</a><font color=#333333> - </font><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary>The Library</a> <font color=#333333> - </font><a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/">The Mage Compendium</a><font color=#333333> - </font>  <br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
